switchamba (0.1.1-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Grab keyboard during word correction so user keys typed mid-replay
    are queued and flushed after, preventing interleaved output.
  * Preserve and restore user's clipboard across Double-Ctrl line
    correction; clear it first to avoid empty-selection fallback to
    prior clipboard content.
  * Add LayoutSwitcher.clear_clipboard and split write_clipboard from
    write_clipboard_and_paste.

