switchamba (0.1.0-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Automatic EN/RU/UA keyboard layout detection and switching.
  * GNOME Shell extension for D-Bus layout control.
  * GTK4/Adwaita setup wizard and settings UI.
  * Systemd user service integration.

